{"tid":2309732,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"數據調查：玩《R6S》《Among US》玩家最聰明，手機玩家IQ平均最低","createTime":"2020-12-02T17:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T05:59:11.000Z","uid":42675,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b160e903926fe2a0c073b5b0a098141ca92a0598","tid":2309732,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFXTyZ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFXTyZ4.png&h=f2cae5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智能商數（intelligence quotient）是用智力測試測量人們在其年齡的認知能力得分，而智商通常也是一般大眾用來判別人的聰明與否，一般來說，有一半的人屬於 90-109 正常平均智力水平，而 110 分以上則為高智商者。如今，有一家海外線上賭場遊戲業者，針對玩家族群進行了抽樣調查，從而公布了一項頗具話題與爭議的結果，手機遊戲玩家的智商平均較低。<br />\n<br />\nRoyal Panda 是一家總部位於地中海島國馬爾他、經營線上賭場的上市公司，該公司在英國也獲得執業許可，最近他們透過對 1,001 名玩家與科技產品使用者進行智力測驗，主要以言語智力（Verbal Intelligence）、數理能力（Mathematical Ability）、邏輯推理（Logical Reasoning）、視覺推理（Visual Reasoning）四個部份進行測試，最後依照受測者的遊戲使用平台及習慣統計出結果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbziK65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbziK65.jpg&h=a1f4362e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有趣的是，這份報告還特別統計了許多受測者們玩過的遊戲，列出這些遊戲玩家們的平均智商。從結果顯示，《虹彩六號：圍攻行動》玩家智商平均高達 120.3，而太空狼人殺《Among Us》平均也有 118.9，而需要各種創意的《Minecraft》則有 116.3 分數。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tUCDK7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtUCDK7d.jpg&h=eb1ffc84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jZR47r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jZR47r.jpg&h=01a5c89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從排名往下看，可以發現動作與休閒類型的遊戲來說，普遍智力分數較低，最後一名則是知名的手遊《憤怒鳥》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDYrT0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDYrT0C.jpg&h=afb15be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然，玩家不必要對第三方的數據調查過於認真，畢竟 Royal Panda 並沒有公開抽樣方式與測試過程，某些遊戲也有跨平台（如《Among Us》），因此玩家族群分布的數字結果僅供參考。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/45770/royalpanda-administered-a-4-part-iq-test-to-1001-console-users\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F45770%2Froyalpanda-administered-a-4-part-iq-test-to-1001-console-users&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=fa4a2d08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/45770/royalpanda-administered-a-4-part-iq-test-to-1001-console-users</a>"},{"pid":"55ef8d428b05d16b8e54841e71b0589449d46851","tid":2309732,"uid":33132,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"打r6真係少啲腦都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a26f267e179808467430e1a25c55a7daa4af1c","tid":2309732,"uid":154505,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"R6=智力 視力 聽力 創造力 記憶力 檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce86cb31c2051f4a6a4b0185f84684f004bc2ea5","tid":2309732,"uid":243208,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:00:53.000Z","msg":"玩跑online法老王先最聰明"},{"pid":"4a145d288328b721c2c8cd3c66d22a60f1f58a36","tid":2309732,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:05:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63f02601a8b77eb7ed494a65bb3a88a8a800ea75","tid":2309732,"uid":42675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a145d288328b721c2c8cd3c66d22a60f1f58a36","tid":2309732,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:05:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:06:50.000Z","msg":"COD係冇R6高姐<br />\n後面仲有成堆低過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nSdO7qb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSdO7qb.jpg&h=37656681&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acb107d6341c19c95c3d298f8ca479b403436373","tid":2309732,"uid":159367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci